  "text": "This meta-analysis was conducted in accordance with the preferred reporting items for systematic reviews and metaanalyses guidelines, [CITATION_1] and based on published studies with ethical approvals. No original clinical raw data was collected in this analysis, thus ethical approval was not necessary.",
